{DescAliveShort}{}{Despite her green hair and a scar, you can guess, that she is working as a bartender here.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{It's Mira. She's mixing a cocktail.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{She's young and pretty, but it's enough to look into her eyes, to make clear, that she won't accept any harassment. Take a look into her eyes and at knuckleduster necklace on her neck.}
